 BR-01: Checkout Proceeds with Empty Cart

Severity: High

Environment: https://www.saucedemo.com/

 Steps to Reproduce:
1. Login with valid credentials
2. Do not add any product to cart
3. Click cart icon
4. Click "Checkout"
5. Enter First Name, Last Name, and Zip/Postal Code
6. Click "Continue"
7. Click "Finish"

Expected Result: 
System should prevent checkout when cart is empty and display an appropriate validation message.

Actual Result:  
System allows checkout process to complete even when no products are added to cart.

Impact: 
Users are able to complete invalid checkout flow with no selected products.

Status: Fail


